  "text": "tested. Recently, we identified potentially functional E. coli asRNAs based on their ability to form dsRNA with their sense counterparts in vivo. [CITATION_1] Hfq, as an important player mediating RNA-RNA interactions, is a plausible candidate for mediation of massive dsRNA formation. Whether Hfq is an essential factor for the formation of sense/antisense pairs remains to be tested.",
